Titolo: Dance Dance Revolution Hottest Party 3

Anno: 2009

Descrizione: Dance Dance Revolution Hottest Party 3 is a rhythm-based dancing game for the Wii. It is a video game released by Konami in 2009. The game can be played using a dance pad, the classic controller, or the Wii Remote and Nunchuck combination. It has two games preceding it: Dance Dance Revolution Hottest Party and Dance Dance Revolution Hottest Party 2.

